        <h1>Info Desk Triage — Interactive Guide</h1>
        <div class="lead">Fast lookup for student employees: contacts, in-person scripts, and email templates.</div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid">
      <main>
        <section class="card" aria-labelledby="searchTitle">
          <h2 id="searchTitle">Search topics & templates</h2>
          <p class="small">Type a keyword like "financial aid", "transcripts", or "student ID" to quickly find the right contact and template.</p>

          <label for="q">Quick search</label>
          <input type="search" id="q" placeholder="search topics, e.g. 'financial aid'" aria-label="Search topics" />

          <div class="search-result" id="results"></div>
        </section>

        <section class="card" style="margin-top:12px" id="topicPanel">
          <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">
            <h2 style="font-size:16px;margin:0">Selected Topic</h2>
            <div class="small" id="topicMeta"></div>
          </div>
          <div id="topicContent" style="margin-top:10px">
            <p class="small">Choose a topic from the left or use search to begin. Each topic includes: contact, in-person script, and email template you can copy or send.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
          <h2 style="font-size:16px;margin:0">Triage Flow</h2>
          <div class="small">Simple decision flow to help determine next steps when a visitor approaches the desk.</div>
          <div class="flow" id="triageFlow">
            <div class="step">1. Ask: "How can I help you today?"</div>
            <div class="step">2. Identify need: Admissions / Financial Aid / ID / Transcripts</div>
            <div class="step">3. Quick Fix? (Yes → assist) (No → refer)</div>
            <div class="step">4. Use template or escalate to department</div>
            <div class="step">5. Document & follow up if needed</div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <aside>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Quick Topics</h3>
          <div class="small">Click to open — templates will appear on the main panel.</div>
          <div id="topicsList" style="margin-top:10px"></div>
          <div class="aside-actions">
            <button class="btn" id="showAll">Show All Templates</button>
            <button class="btn ghost" id="printBtn">Print / Save PDF</button>
            <button class="btn ghost" id="exportCSV">Export Templates (CSV)</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
          <h3>Contacts</h3>
          <div id="contacts" style="margin-top:8px"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
          <h3>Shortcuts</h3>
          <div class="small">Actions</div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:8px">
            <button class="btn ghost" id="copyAll">Copy Selected Template</button>
            <button class="btn" id="openMail">Open Mail Compose</button>
          </div>
        </div>
